rows.label: qev086001_MSG0001
rows.name: Something wrong, Linly? Tatsu not hear any chopping.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0002
rows.name:
And Tatsu is dying of hunger.
Linly doesn't want to be murderer, does Linly?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0003
rows.name: Oh, sorry. I'll whip something up here real quick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0004
rows.name: He's right, Lin. You seem a little off today.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0006
rows.name:
It's just... We detected a transmission loss
in the industrial-district energy system.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0007
rows.name: You repaired that before, right? How much of a loss?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0009
rows.name: That sounds well within safety tolerances.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0010
rows.name: Yeah it is. It's not that so much...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0011
rows.name:
It's just the upgrades I installed
should be working better than that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0012
rows.name: It should've been a year till we detected any loss whatsoever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0013
rows.name: Ah...so it's a mechanic's pride, is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086001_MSG0014
rows.name:
Sounds like a worthy mission.
Why don't we go run some diagnostics?[ST:wait ]
